{
  "title": "Chewy Norwegian Sugar Crumble",
  "description": "A salty, chewy, comforting norwegian dish featuring dark brown soft sugar that caramelizes and pairs well with savory dishes or as a low-carb snack.",
  "cuisine": "Norwegian",
  "diet": [
